name: 普雷斯顿·奥布赖恩
name_full: 普雷斯顿·奥布赖恩 Preston O'Brien

last_movies.title: 指环王：力量之戒 第一季

introduction: Preston grew up in the suburb of Morningside Auckland New Zealand. The suburb made famous by the television show BroTown. He started acting in his mid thirties. His theatre debut was for 'The Smell of Rain' as part of the Short&Sweet theatre competition where his play won three awards.Crackheads was his first feature film.
